{
  "driverId": "{{driverId}}"
}

### Assign Vehicle to Delivery
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/deliveries/{{deliveryId}}/assign-vehicle
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleId": "{{vehicleId}}"
}

